CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 20, 1971, pg. 17 reads: "Mrs. Alma Powell, a secretary in Gateway Four, is the wife of popular disc jockey and Director of Public Relations for Radio Station WAMO. The couple reside in East Liberty."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Alma Powell modeling dark crushed velvet suit, in front of plain curtain
